The LaTeX style used in this book is an adaptation of The Legrand Orange Book Template.

---

The Legrand Orange Book Version 1.4 (12/4/14) was used as template.
The template was downloaded from: http://www.LaTeXTemplates.com
The original author of The Legrand Orange Book template is:
Mathias Legrand (legrand.mathias@gmail.com)
The original license of The Legrand Orange Book Template is:
CC BY-NC-SA 3.0  (http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/)

